{"tid":1292582,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲狗會泯滅人性去咬人? - 路西法效應","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:28:12.000Z","uid":131731,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24431268b01461840cfcff05449559390fd17644","tid":1292582,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2X5W8mM_Wek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2X5W8mM_Wek&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=07004ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2X5W8mM_Wek</a><br />\n條片有啲長, 總括咗黑警點解會越黎越冇人性<br />\n<br />\n其中最大嘅原因就係匿名化之後去個人化同埋去人性化<br />\n<br />\n冇number之下佢地已經唔當自己係一個人, 而係一個對抗示威者(敵人)嘅機器, 所以乜都做得出<br />\n<br />\n當當權者都喺背後助長佢地嘅殘忍行為時, 班仆街就更加覺得自己做嘅野係啱, 越墮越深<br />\n<br />\n而我地抗爭者亦都會慢慢染上無力感, 變得盲目順從<br />\n<br />\n但到呢一刻, 我feel到我地嘅無力感開始慢慢減退, 抗爭者開始識得同埋願意去反抗<br />\n<br />\n所以, 大家真係要去認知當權者並唔會係永遠都啱(啲藍絲受呢個思想影響得極深!), 亦都要記住每個人都係有能力去推翻暴政. <br />\n<br />\n至於黑警嘅局面, 我相信只有推翻個政權先能夠解決, 班仆街偽進仔係完全唔會思考任何野."},{"pid":"fe01324a097bba970cf502dca285587b70b57c0e","tid":1292582,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd04a89501ebfe943b3fdc1fd50db78b38337b","tid":1292582,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dbdad02bdc970ace79c61c49b283b140be1ff6","tid":1292582,"uid":168381,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"岩岩小學畢業？有邊個唔識"},{"pid":"d1fdee346d291795971703c838b2700f7a32b626","tid":1292582,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5dbdad02bdc970ace79c61c49b283b140be1ff6","tid":1292582,"uid":168381,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2